    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A solution of resin in a volatile solvent; usually made of a soft resin such as mastic or sandarac, dissolved in turpentine or alcohol; characteristically brittle when dry and not very durable.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000016491/Gettens and Stout, Painting Materials (1966)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Solución de una resina en un solvente volátil, habitualmente una resina blanda como mástic o sandáraca disuelta en trementina o alcohol. Característicamente quebradiza al secarse y no muy duradera.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hars opgelost in een vluchtig oplosmiddel; wordt doorgaans gemaakt door een zachte harssoort zoals mastiek of sandarak op te lossen in terpentijn of alcohol; is in verharde vorm erg broos en niet erg duurzaam.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種由樹脂溶於可揮發溶劑中而成的溶液，通常以如瑪蒂脂或山達脂的軟性樹脂溶於松節油或酒精而成，其特色為乾燥時發脆易碎，並不持久耐用。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
